@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_vwpwkp(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = ((wp.cos(tmp + 0.80) / 0.81) - wp.cos(wp.sin(v0 + 0.40)))
    v0 = wp.sin(((v1 + 0.69 / v1 + 0.68) - v2))
    v1 = tmp
    tmp = wp.exp((v0 + wp.sin(v2 + 0.57)))
    tmp = wp.sin(wp.cos((v0 + 0.62 / v1 + 0.27)))
    v1 = v2
    v0 = (wp.exp((tmp + 0.09 - v1 + 0.52)) * (0.84 + (tmp + 0.29 - v2 + 0.00)))
    data[tid] = v0
